                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7329" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1141</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8834 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被迫进入TCL家族：奥马电器反收购防线为何被突破？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Forced to enter the TCL family: Why is Oma Electric&#39;s anti acquisition defense line broken through?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李金茹，邓昊宇，辛鹏起，李鑫奇，孔利，刘家阳，李可心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东奥马电器股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恶意收购；反收购；控制权；奥马电器；TCL</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Malicious acquisition; Anti takeover; control power; Omar Electric; TCL</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恶意收购事件在中国市场中屡见不鲜，与之对应的反收购却还没有建立起完整的防御体系，大多数企业的反收购意识略显薄弱。2021年1月TCL集团从奥马电器“零持股”开始增持，最终五个月内拿下奥马电器控制权，成为其实控人。由赵国栋实控的奥马电器曾作为白电产业的领跑者，至此黯然退场。案例介绍了并购双方的背景，奥马电器的控制权争夺之战的过程，重点描述了奥马电器原实控人与TCL集团展开的数次收购攻防战。希望通过该案例，为我国其他上市公司预防恶意收购敲响警钟，引导学员思考是何机缘引发TCL突袭成功，奥马电器的一系列反收购防线为何被突破，从而进一步思考反收购措施的完善空间。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Malicious takeover events are common in the Chinese market, but the corresponding anti takeover has not yet established a complete defense system, and the anti takeover awareness of most enterprises is slightly weak. In January 2021, TCL Group began to increase its shareholding from &quot;zero shareholding&quot; of Oma Electric, and finally took control of Oma Electric within five months, becoming its actual controller. Omar Electric, which is controlled by Zhao Guodong, once took the lead in white electricity industry, and now it has exited. The case introduces the background of both sides of the merger and acquisition, the process of the battle for control of Oma Electric, and focuses on several acquisition battles between the original controller of Oma Electric and TCL Group. It is hoped that through the studying of this case, it will ring an alarm for other listed companies in China to prevent malicious takeover, guide students to think about what opportunities led to the success of TCL&#39;s surprise attack, and Why has Oma Electric broken through a series of anti acquisition defenses, so as to think deeply the improvement space of Anti Acquisition.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》、《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恶意收购的时机选择；反收购动因；反收购手段；预防与抵制反收购措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-05</td>
                            </tr>
